{"tid":2435473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民打小人 狂揪 習翠翠、忠誠廢物","createTime":"2021-03-06T09:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T09:11:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfca63d156bf3f0abab6f3cffec94323c26b4bf","tid":2435473,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210306/7DTTCWRLDNEOLF77CCTTUK6FQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210306%2F7DTTCWRLDNEOLF77CCTTUK6FQI%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=f9dcc72c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210306%2F7DTTCWRLDNEOLF77CCTTUK6FQI%2F&h=a5315c14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210306/7DTTCWRLDNEOLF77CCTTUK6FQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民打小人 狂揪 習翠翠、忠誠廢物<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日是二十四節氣中的春季節氣「驚蟄」，有民眾按照傳統到灣仔鵝頸橋打小人。小人當道致民怨四起，47名被控告串謀顛覆國家政權罪的民主派人士前晚更須全數還柙候審。有人首次到場輪候，表明要痛打特首林鄭月娥、律政司長鄭若驊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hJaLjT3HlxVyaVW4QpSPbQQQxN0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DNVYAJUPNBFM5F66OKJBC7VW3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhJaLjT3HlxVyaVW4QpSPbQQQxN0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDNVYAJUPNBFM5F66OKJBC7VW3Y.jpg&h=071734c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳先生在寶牒上寫上「香港人加油，手足頂住」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方一度查看<br />\n<br />\n灣仔鵝頸橋底多個打小人攤檔昨早已大排長龍，民眾手持香燭、寶牒及小人紙輪。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。除在小人紙上寫上「大波樺」、「7婆」、「習翠翠」、「3萬黑警」及「忠誠廢物」等政府高官及警隊外號外 ，他亦在寶牒上寫上「香港人加油，手足頂住」，警方一度上前查看。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Nz0m3ZUhhvSjMcon62nLSOS44bo=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BOAEY425YVE6HOOENAXRU2MF3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNz0m3ZUhhvSjMcon62nLSOS44bo%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBOAEY425YVE6HOOENAXRU2MF3A.jpg&h=028a6b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鵝頸橋多個打小人攤檔昨大排長龍。<br />\n<br />\n同樣首次排隊打小人的李先生指明要痛打林鄭月娥、鄭若驊及兩人的家屬。他批。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐也說，。。。。。。。。，「打政務司定律政司啊⋯⋯我唔記得嗰條友（的名字），總言之最肥嗰兩個喇，坐爆凳嗰兩個。」<br />\n<br />\n自言已十年沒打過小人的馬先生則表示，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sdeyk8ZRGcwboZ2lezJA81o092c=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GML56EA6N5BI7CQYAFXZVBY6YI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fsdeyk8ZRGcwboZ2lezJA81o092c%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGML56EA6N5BI7CQYAFXZVBY6YI.jpg&h=22f17d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「小人婆」手起鞋落，拍打聲不絕。"}]}